\begin{center}
{\bf  Exact conserved quantities on the cylinder II: off-critical case.}\\
\vspace{1.8cm}
{\large D.\ Fioravanti $^a$ and M.\ Rossi $^b$ \footnote{E-mail:
Davide.Fioravanti@durham.ac.uk, M.Rossi@ma.hw.ac.uk}}\\ \vspace{.5cm}
